This album is slightly underwhelming. I was expecting a little more since I heard Domino the Destitute. A lot of the songs are soft or feel like intros. Vic the Butcher and Domino are the only worthy songs, but maybe it will grow on me.

Thanks for the upload nominae... no one else had it or were nice enough to upload it, so screw all those people complaining about your upload.

As for the album, just from a quick listen it is light years better than YotBR, a lot of the riffs remind me of Good Apollo Vol. I.

Also, comparing Coheed to Rush is just stupid...
